title: Warriors player consultant Nash makes big impact right away
text:
Photo: Liz Hafalia, The Chronicle Player development consultant Steve Nash works with Warriors guard Klay Thompson at the Warriors gym in Oakland, Calif., on Friday, October 2, 2015. Player development consultant Steve Nash works with Warriors guard...
There’s little doubt that Steve Nash will make Stephen Curry better at reading defenses, that he will make Klay Thompson a better ball-handler and that he will make Harrison Barnes a more efficient player.
